    "Techniques based on language models can be used in natural language generation, machine translation, speech recognition, text classification and other tasks.",
    "At the same time, natural language generation technology has also been widely concerned and applied, such as: automatic summary, [13][14][15][16]chatbot, text generation and so on.In addition, deep learning techniques can also be used for tasks such as syntax analysis, semantic analysis, and named entity recognition.",
